org.sql: SELECT changesets.* FROM changesets WHERE changesets.repository_id = "$1" AND scmid IN ('899a15dba03a3b350b89c3f537e4bbe02a03cdc9', '7234cb2750b63f47bff735edc50a1c0a433c2518') ORDER BY changesets.committed_on DESC, changesets.id DESC, committed_on DESC
